		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_7&quot; title=&quot;December 7&quot;&gt;December 7&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;:  &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Armed_Forces_Flag_Day&quot; title=&quot;Armed Forces Flag Day&quot;&gt;Armed Forces Flag Day&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; in India; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/National_Pearl_Harbor_Remembrance_Day&quot; title=&quot;National Pearl Harbor Remembrance Day&quot;&gt;Pearl Harbor Day&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; in the United States
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 100px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:Jesse_james_portrait.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;Jesse James&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Jesse James&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/22/Jesse_james_portrait.jpg/100px-Jesse_james_portrait.jpg&quot; width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;138&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/22/Jesse_james_portrait.jpg/150px-Jesse_james_portrait.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/22/Jesse_james_portrait.jpg/200px-Jesse_james_portrait.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;1115&quot; data-file-height=&quot;1536&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;Jesse James&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1815&quot; title=&quot;1815&quot;&gt;1815&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Michel_Ney&quot; title=&quot;Michel Ney&quot;&gt;Michel Ney&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Marshal_of_France&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot; title=&quot;Marshal of France&quot;&gt;Marshal of France&lt;/a&gt;, was executed by a firing squad near Paris' &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Jardin_du_Luxembourg&quot; title=&quot;Jardin du Luxembourg&quot;&gt;Jardin du Luxembourg&lt;/a&gt; for supporting &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Napoleon&quot; title=&quot;Napoleon&quot;&gt;Napoleon&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1869&quot; title=&quot;1869&quot;&gt;1869&lt;/a&gt; – American outlaw &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Jesse_James&quot; title=&quot;Jesse James&quot;&gt;Jesse James&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;i&gt;(pictured)&lt;/i&gt; committed his first confirmed bank robbery in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Gallatin,_Missouri&quot; title=&quot;Gallatin, Missouri&quot;&gt;Gallatin, Missouri&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1936&quot; title=&quot;1936&quot;&gt;1936&lt;/a&gt; – Australian &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Cricket&quot; title=&quot;Cricket&quot;&gt;cricketer&lt;/a&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Jack_Fingleton&quot; title=&quot;Jack Fingleton&quot;&gt;Jack Fingleton&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; became the first player to score &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Century_(cricket)&quot; title=&quot;Century (cricket)&quot;&gt;centuries&lt;/a&gt; in four consecutive &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Test_cricket&quot; title=&quot;Test cricket&quot;&gt;Test&lt;/a&gt; innings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1946&quot; title=&quot;1946&quot;&gt;1946&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Winecoff_Hotel_fire&quot; title=&quot;Winecoff Hotel fire&quot;&gt;deadliest hotel fire in U.S. history&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; happened at the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Winecoff_Hotel&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot; title=&quot;Winecoff Hotel&quot;&gt;Winecoff Hotel&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Atlanta&quot; title=&quot;Atlanta&quot;&gt;Atlanta, Georgia&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1988&quot; title=&quot;1988&quot;&gt;1988&lt;/a&gt; – A &lt;span class=&quot;nowrap&quot;&gt;6.9 &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Moment_magnitude_scale&quot; title=&quot;Moment magnitude scale&quot;&gt;M&lt;sub&gt;w&lt;/sub&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; earthquake &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1988_Armenian_earthquake&quot; title=&quot;1988 Armenian earthquake&quot;&gt;struck&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Spitak&quot; title=&quot;Spitak&quot;&gt;Spitak&lt;/a&gt; region of Armenia, killing at least 25,000 people.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_6&quot; title=&quot;December 6&quot;&gt;December 6&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_7&quot; title=&quot;December 7&quot;&gt;December 7&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_8&quot; title=&quot;December 8&quot;&gt;December 8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;otd-footer hlist noprint&quot; style=&quot;text-align: right;&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Wikipedia:Selected_anniversaries/December&quot; title=&quot;Wikipedia:Selected anniversaries/December&quot;&gt;Archive&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://lists.wikimedia.org/mailman/listinfo/daily-article-l&quot; class=&quot;extiw&quot; title=&quot;mail:daily-article-l&quot;&gt;By email&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
