	<entry>
		<id>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FeedItem/onthisday/20161209000000/en</id>
		<title>On this day: December 9</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FeedItem/onthisday/20161209000000/en"/>
				<updated>2016-12-09T00:00:00Z</updated>
		
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_9&quot; title=&quot;December 9&quot;&gt;December 9&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;: 100th birthday of actor &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Kirk_Douglas&quot; title=&quot;Kirk Douglas&quot;&gt;Kirk Douglas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; 
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 100px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:Ottoman_surrender_of_Jerusalem_restored.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;The surrender of Jerusalem&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;The surrender of Jerusalem&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/55/Ottoman_surrender_of_Jerusalem_restored.jpg/100px-Ottoman_surrender_of_Jerusalem_restored.jpg&quot; width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;131&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/55/Ottoman_surrender_of_Jerusalem_restored.jpg/150px-Ottoman_surrender_of_Jerusalem_restored.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/55/Ottoman_surrender_of_Jerusalem_restored.jpg/200px-Ottoman_surrender_of_Jerusalem_restored.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;2995&quot; data-file-height=&quot;3913&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;The surrender of Jerusalem&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1872&quot; title=&quot;1872&quot;&gt;1872&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/P._B._S._Pinchback&quot; title=&quot;P. B. S. Pinchback&quot;&gt;P. B. S. Pinchback&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; took office as &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/List_of_Governors_of_Louisiana&quot; title=&quot;List of Governors of Louisiana&quot;&gt;Governor of Louisiana&lt;/a&gt;, the first &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/African_American&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot; title=&quot;African American&quot;&gt;African American&lt;/a&gt; governor of a U.S. state.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1905&quot; title=&quot;1905&quot;&gt;1905&lt;/a&gt; – Legislation establishing &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/State_secularism&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot; title=&quot;State secularism&quot;&gt;state secularism&lt;/a&gt; in France &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1905_French_law_on_the_Separation_of_the_Churches_and_the_State&quot; title=&quot;1905 French law on the Separation of the Churches and the State&quot;&gt;was passed&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; by the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Chamber_of_Deputies_of_France&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot; title=&quot;Chamber of Deputies of France&quot;&gt;Chamber of Deputies of France&lt;/a&gt;, triggering &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Civil_disobedience&quot; title=&quot;Civil disobedience&quot;&gt;civil disobedience&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Roman_Catholicism_in_France&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot; title=&quot;Roman Catholicism in France&quot;&gt;French Catholics&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1917&quot; title=&quot;1917&quot;&gt;1917&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/World_War_I&quot; title=&quot;World War I&quot;&gt;First World War&lt;/a&gt;: &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Hussein_al-Husayni&quot; title=&quot;Hussein al-Husayni&quot;&gt;Hussein al-Husayni&lt;/a&gt;, the Ottoman &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Mayor_of_Jerusalem&quot; title=&quot;Mayor of Jerusalem&quot;&gt;mayor of Jerusalem&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Battle_of_Jerusalem&quot; title=&quot;Battle of Jerusalem&quot;&gt;surrendered&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;i&gt;(pictured)&lt;/i&gt; the city to the British.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1948&quot; title=&quot;1948&quot;&gt;1948&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/United_Nations_General_Assembly&quot; title=&quot;United Nations General Assembly&quot;&gt;United Nations General Assembly&lt;/a&gt; adopted the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Genocide_Convention&quot; title=&quot;Genocide Convention&quot;&gt;Genocide Convention&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, which defines &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Genocide&quot; title=&quot;Genocide&quot;&gt;genocide&lt;/a&gt; in legal terms and advises its signatories to prevent and punish such actions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1968&quot; title=&quot;1968&quot;&gt;1968&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Douglas_Engelbart&quot; title=&quot;Douglas Engelbart&quot;&gt;Douglas Engelbart&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; gave what became known as &quot;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/The_Mother_of_All_Demos&quot; title=&quot;The Mother of All Demos&quot;&gt;The Mother of All Demos&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&quot;, publicly debuting the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Mouse_(computer)&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot; title=&quot;Mouse (computer)&quot;&gt;computer mouse&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Hypertext&quot; title=&quot;Hypertext&quot;&gt;hypertext&lt;/a&gt;, and the bit-mapped &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Graphical_user_interface&quot; title=&quot;Graphical user interface&quot;&gt;graphical user interface&lt;/a&gt; using the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/NLS_(computer_system)&quot; title=&quot;NLS (computer system)&quot;&gt;oN-Line System (NLS)&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_8&quot; title=&quot;December 8&quot;&gt;December 8&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_9&quot; title=&quot;December 9&quot;&gt;December 9&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_10&quot; title=&quot;December 10&quot;&gt;December 10&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
