		<title>On this day: December 10</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FeedItem/onthisday/20161210000000/en"/>
				<updated>2016-12-10T00:00:00Z</updated>
		
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_10&quot; title=&quot;December 10&quot;&gt;December 10&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;: &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Human_Rights_Day&quot; title=&quot;Human Rights Day&quot;&gt;Human Rights Day&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 100px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:Wallis_Simpson_-1936.JPG&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;Wallis Simpson&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Wallis Simpson&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/33/Wallis_Simpson_-1936.JPG/100px-Wallis_Simpson_-1936.JPG&quot; width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;127&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/33/Wallis_Simpson_-1936.JPG/150px-Wallis_Simpson_-1936.JPG 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/3/33/Wallis_Simpson_-1936.JPG/200px-Wallis_Simpson_-1936.JPG 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;471&quot; data-file-height=&quot;597&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;Wallis Simpson&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1799&quot; title=&quot;1799&quot;&gt;1799&lt;/a&gt; – France became the first country to &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/History_of_the_metric_system&quot; title=&quot;History of the metric system&quot;&gt;adopt&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Metric_system&quot; title=&quot;Metric system&quot;&gt;metric system&lt;/a&gt; as its system for weights and measures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1898&quot; title=&quot;1898&quot;&gt;1898&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Spanish%E2%80%93American_War&quot; title=&quot;Spanish–American War&quot;&gt;Spanish–American War&lt;/a&gt; ended with the signing of the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Treaty_of_Paris_(1898)&quot; title=&quot;Treaty of Paris (1898)&quot;&gt;Treaty of Paris&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, with Spain recognizing the independence of Cuba; and ceding Guam, the Philippines, and Puerto Rico to the United States.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1936&quot; title=&quot;1936&quot;&gt;1936&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Edward_VIII&quot; title=&quot;Edward VIII&quot;&gt;Edward VIII&lt;/a&gt;, desiring to marry American &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Socialite&quot; title=&quot;Socialite&quot;&gt;socialite&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Wallis,_Duchess_of_Windsor&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot; title=&quot;Wallis, Duchess of Windsor&quot;&gt;Wallis Simpson&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i&gt;(pictured)&lt;/i&gt; against widespread opposition, &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Edward_VIII_abdication_crisis&quot; title=&quot;Edward VIII abdication crisis&quot;&gt;abdicated the throne&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, the only British monarch to have voluntarily done so since the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Anglo-Saxons&quot; title=&quot;Anglo-Saxons&quot;&gt;Anglo-Saxon&lt;/a&gt; period.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1941&quot; title=&quot;1941&quot;&gt;1941&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/World_War_II&quot; title=&quot;World War II&quot;&gt;Second World War&lt;/a&gt;: &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Imperial_Japanese_Navy&quot; title=&quot;Imperial Japanese Navy&quot;&gt;Imperial Japanese Navy&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Torpedo_bomber&quot; title=&quot;Torpedo bomber&quot;&gt;torpedo bombers&lt;/a&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Sinking_of_Prince_of_Wales_and_Repulse&quot; title=&quot;Sinking of Prince of Wales and Repulse&quot;&gt;sank&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Royal_Navy&quot; title=&quot;Royal Navy&quot;&gt;Royal Navy&lt;/a&gt; capital ships &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/HMS_Prince_of_Wales_(53)&quot; title=&quot;HMS Prince of Wales (53)&quot;&gt;HMS&amp;#160;&lt;i&gt;Prince of Wales&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/HMS_Repulse_(1916)&quot; title=&quot;HMS Repulse (1916)&quot;&gt;HMS&amp;#160;&lt;i&gt;Repulse&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/a&gt; east of &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Peninsular_Malaysia&quot; title=&quot;Peninsular Malaysia&quot;&gt;Malaya&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1989&quot; title=&quot;1989&quot;&gt;1989&lt;/a&gt; – At the first open pro-democracy demonstration in Mongolia, journalist &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Tsakhiagiin_Elbegdorj&quot; title=&quot;Tsakhiagiin Elbegdorj&quot;&gt;Tsakhiagiin Elbegdorj&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; announced the formation of the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Mongolian_Democratic_Union&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot; title=&quot;Mongolian Democratic Union&quot;&gt;Mongolian Democratic Union&lt;/a&gt;, which would be instrumental in ending Communist rule four months later.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_9&quot; title=&quot;December 9&quot;&gt;December 9&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_10&quot; title=&quot;December 10&quot;&gt;December 10&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_11&quot; title=&quot;December 11&quot;&gt;December 11&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;otd-footer hlist noprint&quot; style=&quot;text-align: right;&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Wikipedia:Selected_anniversaries/December&quot; title=&quot;Wikipedia:Selected anniversaries/December&quot;&gt;Archive&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://lists.wikimedia.org/mailman/listinfo/daily-article-l&quot; class=&quot;extiw&quot; title=&quot;mail:daily-article-l&quot;&gt;By email&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/List_of_historical_anniversaries&quot; title=&quot;List of historical anniversaries&quot;&gt;List of historical anniversaries&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: smaller;&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; Current date: &lt;span class=&quot;nowrap&quot;&gt;December 10, 2016&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Coordinated_Universal_Time&quot; title=&quot;Coordinated Universal Time&quot;&gt;UTC&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;plainlinks&quot; id=&quot;otd-purgelink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nowrap&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;external text&quot; href=&quot;//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=MediaWiki:Ffeed-onthisday-transcludeme&amp;amp;action=purge&quot;&gt;Reload this page&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
</summary>
