	<entry>
		<id>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FeedItem/onthisday/20161211000000/en</id>
		<title>On this day: December 11</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FeedItem/onthisday/20161211000000/en"/>
				<updated>2016-12-11T00:00:00Z</updated>
		
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_11&quot; title=&quot;December 11&quot;&gt;December 11&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;: &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Mawlid&quot; title=&quot;Mawlid&quot;&gt;Mawlid&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; begins at sunset (&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Sunni_Islam&quot; title=&quot;Sunni Islam&quot;&gt;Sunni Islam&lt;/a&gt;, 2016); &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Republic_Day&quot; title=&quot;Republic Day&quot;&gt;Republic Day&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Burkina_Faso&quot; title=&quot;Burkina Faso&quot;&gt;Burkina Faso&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; (&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1958&quot; title=&quot;1958&quot;&gt;1958&lt;/a&gt;)
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 100px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:Shulyavska_respublika.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;Monument to the workers of the Shuliavka Republic&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Monument to the workers of the Shuliavka Republic&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d1/Shulyavska_respublika.jpg/100px-Shulyavska_respublika.jpg&quot; width=&quot;100&quot; height=&quot;149&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d1/Shulyavska_respublika.jpg/150px-Shulyavska_respublika.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d1/Shulyavska_respublika.jpg/200px-Shulyavska_respublika.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;279&quot; data-file-height=&quot;415&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;Monument to the workers of the Shuliavka Republic&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/220&quot; title=&quot;220&quot;&gt;220&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Emperor_Xian_of_Han&quot; title=&quot;Emperor Xian of Han&quot;&gt;Emperor Xian&lt;/a&gt; abdicated the throne and the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Han_dynasty&quot; title=&quot;Han dynasty&quot;&gt;Han dynasty&lt;/a&gt; broke apart, beginning the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Three_Kingdoms&quot; title=&quot;Three Kingdoms&quot;&gt;Three Kingdoms&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; period in China.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1899&quot; title=&quot;1899&quot;&gt;1899&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Second_Boer_War&quot; title=&quot;Second Boer War&quot;&gt;Second Boer War&lt;/a&gt;: In the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Battle_of_Magersfontein&quot; title=&quot;Battle of Magersfontein&quot;&gt;Battle of Magersfontein&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Boer&quot; title=&quot;Boer&quot;&gt;Boers&lt;/a&gt; defeated the forces of the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/British_Empire&quot; title=&quot;British Empire&quot;&gt;British Empire&lt;/a&gt; trying to relieve the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Siege_of_Kimberley&quot; title=&quot;Siege of Kimberley&quot;&gt;Siege of Kimberley&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1905&quot; title=&quot;1905&quot;&gt;1905&lt;/a&gt; – In support of the December Uprising in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Moscow&quot; title=&quot;Moscow&quot;&gt;Moscow&lt;/a&gt;, the Council of Workers' Deputies of &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Kiev&quot; title=&quot;Kiev&quot;&gt;Kiev&lt;/a&gt; staged a mass uprising, establishing the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Shuliavka_Republic&quot; title=&quot;Shuliavka Republic&quot;&gt;Shuliavka Republic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;i&gt;(monument pictured)&lt;/i&gt; in the city.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1980&quot; title=&quot;1980&quot;&gt;1980&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/United_States_Congress&quot; title=&quot;United States Congress&quot;&gt;United States Congress&lt;/a&gt; enacted the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Superfund&quot; title=&quot;Superfund&quot;&gt;Comprehensive Environmental Response, Compensation, and Liability Act&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; to protect people, families, communities and others from heavily contaminated &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Toxic_waste&quot; title=&quot;Toxic waste&quot;&gt;toxic waste&lt;/a&gt; sites that have been abandoned.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/2006&quot; title=&quot;2006&quot;&gt;2006&lt;/a&gt; – The first action in the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Mexican_Drug_War&quot; title=&quot;Mexican Drug War&quot;&gt;Mexican Drug War&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; took place as President &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Felipe_Calder%C3%B3n&quot; title=&quot;Felipe Calderón&quot;&gt;Felipe Calderón&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Operation_Michoacan&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot; title=&quot;Operation Michoacan&quot;&gt;ordered&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Military_of_Mexico&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot; title=&quot;Military of Mexico&quot;&gt;Mexican military&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Federal_Police_(Mexico)&quot; title=&quot;Federal Police (Mexico)&quot;&gt;Federal Police&lt;/a&gt; units into the state of &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Michoac%C3%A1n&quot; title=&quot;Michoacán&quot;&gt;Michoacán&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_10&quot; title=&quot;December 10&quot;&gt;December 10&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_11&quot; title=&quot;December 11&quot;&gt;December 11&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_12&quot; title=&quot;December 12&quot;&gt;December 12&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;otd-footer hlist noprint&quot; style=&quot;text-align: right;&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Wikipedia:Selected_anniversaries/December&quot; title=&quot;Wikipedia:Selected anniversaries/December&quot;&gt;Archive&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://lists.wikimedia.org/mailman/listinfo/daily-article-l&quot; class=&quot;extiw&quot; title=&quot;mail:daily-article-l&quot;&gt;By email&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/List_of_historical_anniversaries&quot; title=&quot;List of historical anniversaries&quot;&gt;List of historical anniversaries&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: smaller;&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt; Current date: &lt;span class=&quot;nowrap&quot;&gt;December 11, 2016&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Coordinated_Universal_Time&quot; title=&quot;Coordinated Universal Time&quot;&gt;UTC&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;plainlinks&quot; id=&quot;otd-purgelink&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nowrap&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;external text&quot; href=&quot;//en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=MediaWiki:Ffeed-onthisday-transcludeme&amp;amp;action=purge&quot;&gt;Reload this page&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
